OL,6,FA schoolgirl felt "stalked" by a
OL,7,Fteenager who then followed her around
OL,8,Ftown after school and stabbed her to
OL,9,Fdeath, jurors have been told.
OL,11,FHolly Newton, 15, was killed by a boy
OL,12,Fwho was carrying a kitchen knife in a
OL,13,Fconfrontation in Hexham,
OL,14,FNorthumberland, it is claimed.
OL,16,FNewcastle Crown Court heard Holly was
OL,17,Frepeatedly stabbed in a back lane and
OL,18,Fwhen a 16-year-old boy tried to step
OL,19,Fin to help her, he was also stabbed.
