OL,3,CSchoolgirl felt "stalked" by teenager
OL,4,Cwho stabbed her to death, jurors told
OL,6,FThe court heard that after the
OL,7,Fstabbing, the boy - who cannot be
OL,8,Fnamed because of his age - briefly
OL,9,Fstarted to cry and said: "Oh, what
OL,10,Fhave I done?"
OL,12,FProsecutor David Brooke KC told the
OL,13,Fcourt the teen had been trying to
OL,14,Fspeak to Holly before her death.
OL,16,FHolly told a friend in a message on
OL,17,Fthe morning that she died: "So he's
OL,18,Fbasically stalking me at this point."
OL,19,FShe also said: "He's going to follow
OL,20,Fme until I talk to him."
