OL,3,CSchoolgirl felt "stalked" by teenager
OL,4,Cwho stabbed her to death, jurors told
OL,6,FThe court heard Holly suffered 36
OL,7,Finjuries caused by the knife, which
OL,8,Fbroke during the attack, that lasted
OL,9,Fat least one minute.
OL,11,FMr Brooke said 12 of them were stab
OL,12,Fwounds, to her face, head, back and
OL,13,Fchest, and 19 others were caused by a
OL,14,F"slashing motion", including five to
OL,15,Fher hands, where she had tried to stop
OL,16,Fthe attack.
OL,18,FA 17-year-old denies the murder of
OL,19,FHolly and wounding charges in relation
OL,20,Fto the boy.
